<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="Dumbbell-Back-Wrist-Curl">Dumbbell Back Wrist Curl</h3>



<p>The <a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/dumbbell-back-wrist-curl" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">dumbbell back wrist curl</a> uses small wrist movements but performs them behind the back. Your arms come down straight with the dumbbells next to your glutes.&nbsp;</p>



<p>This shifts the primary exercise focus onto your wrist flexors. The brachialis and brachioradialis perform secondary roles. The dumbbell back wrist curl improves wrist function and builds grip strength.&nbsp;</p>



