<li>Inhale and engage your core. Exhale and flex your wrists to bring the dumbbells up.&nbsp;</li>



<li>Pause briefly at the top position.&nbsp;</li>



<li>Inhale and bring the dumbbells back down under control.&nbsp;</li>
</ol>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading">Tips</h4>



<ul>
<li>Keep your head up and your chest facing forward throughout. This prevents potential neck strain.&nbsp;</li>



